        "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/morrison-nc2/ncv",
        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Numerical code verification MRL 2 acceptance criteria",
        "description": "Solver passes published benchmark verification cases (lid-driven cavity, Poiseuille flow) with documented convergence to analytical solutions. Order-of-accuracy confirmed for relevant flow regimes."
      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent benchmark verification cases demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations for incompressible viscous flow. Published verification reports confirm second-order spatial accuracy, satisfying MRL 2 numerical code verification requirements."
