      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Formal model input uncertainty propagation is scoped out at MRL 2. Key input parameters (fluid viscosity, density, hemolysis model coefficients) are documented with their nominal values and sources. Sensitivity to input variation is acknowledged but full UQ is deferred to higher MRL assessments."
    },
