      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Test sample characterization beyond standard FDA GCBP protocol requirements is scoped out at MRL 2. The glycerol-water blood analog fluid properties are well-characterised in the published literature and the FDA GCBP test protocol. Sample-to-sample variability is not a significant source of uncertainty for this fluid system."
    },
