      "rationale": "Equivalency of input parameters between validation experiments and COU simulations is addressed qualitatively at MRL 2. Boundary conditions for validation and COU cases are drawn from the same FDA GCBP protocol; any differences in operating point are within the documented operating envelope. Formal equivalency metrics are deferred to MRL 3 assessments."
